node.text: Hello, craft lovers! Today we will show you different ways to upgrade your phone by making different unique cases for it! Also, we will make a phone stand near your bed using a #3Dpen. If you want to make a #Popit phone case, we will show you how to do it ;) Just pick a Pop it fidget you want to use! Keep watching to see many other phone case ideas - using a glue gun, a 3D pen, #hydrogel balls, and other stuff. You will also see some ideas for anti-stress phone cases. In addition, we added some #photography and video-making hacks to help you make excellent content for your social media. Have you tried any of these filming #hacks? Let us know in the comments below ;)

node.title: Upgrade Your Phone With These DIYs

node.text: Hey, crafty people all over the world! Let's see some cool #lifehacks that will make your everyday life easier. You will see some helpful kitchen and #cookinghacks. For example, we will show you how to cut eggs in a unique way. It's an excellent idea for decorating dishes. Also, use a teaspoon to remove the shell from an egg quickly. Did you know that you can clean notebook pages from notes with the help of your iron? Keep watching to see how you can easily make nice-shaped #pancakes, cook eggs, peel the eggplant, cut green onions, and more #cookingtips from professional housewives. In this video, you will also find some fun and clever ways to use #zipties and good home #cleaninghacks.

These unusual hacks with toothpaste and toothbrush will surprise you
Hello, crafters! In this video, you will see many random hacks and #crafts with toothpaste and toothbrush. Did you know you can use these things in so many ways? You can add a bit of color to your hair if you use white toothpaste. Use a toothpaste pack as storage for jams, honey, and other edible liquids. Mix toothpaste, glycerin, and almond oil to create a treatment for your feet. Cover your feet with this mix and wear socks for some time. You will see how #healthy and soft your feet are. As you see, you can use toothpaste for your #skin, #hair, #eyebrows, and more. Don't forget to try these helpful tips on your own! In addition, we shared with you some useful cleaning #hacks for your home.

node.text: Hello, craft lovers! Today we will show you different ways to upgrade your phone by making different unique cases for it! Also, we will make a phone stand near your bed using a #3Dpen. If you want to make a #Popit phone case, we will show you how to do it ;) Just pick a Pop it fidget you want to use! Keep watching to see many other phone case ideas - using a glue gun, a 3D pen, #hydrogel balls, and other stuff. You will also see some ideas for anti-stress phone cases. In addition, we added some #photography and video-making hacks to help you make excellent content for your social media. Have you tried any of these filming #hacks? Let us know in the comments below ;)
